{[#]} {[%tqu "En","Black to move.","","","f8b4","This is a very good move now because White has already committed for the cxd5-exd5 exchange.",10,"c6b4","This is the only thing that you need to be careful about: Nb4 doesn't work for Black when cxd5-exd5 has been included:",0]} 6... Bb4+ {This is a very good move now because White has already committed for the cxd5-exd5 exchange.} (6... Nb4 $2 {This is the only thing that you need to be careful about: Nb4 doesn't work for Black when cxd5-exd5 has been included:} 7. O-O Nc2 8. Nh4 $1 $18 {White is winning because our bishop on f5 is hanging.}) 7. Bd2 Bxd2+ 8. Nbxd2 Nf6 9. O-O O-O $132 {Equal playable position. But if we had the same position without the cxd5-exd5 exchange, White would have a pleasant structural advantage.} *

